Yo! Boombox is out tomorrow in all good record stores or direct from us right now!

BUY now here

Soul Jazz Records' big brand new Yo! Boombox has landed and it's a monster. This is the 4th in our Boombox! series on early hip-hop and it's crammed full of more wicked early hip-hop and disco rap tunes, awesome exclusive photos and lots of text!

The album is 3xLP and 2xCD. There is also a one-off special indies only 3xLP + 7" edition.

All the photos on this album are taken from Sophie Bramly's awesome Yo! BOOK also available on Soul Jazz Books
